{"id":62,"ayahs":[{"number":92,"arabic":"لَن تَنَالُوا۟ ٱلْبِرَّ حَتَّىٰ تُنفِقُوا۟ مِمَّا تُحِبُّونَ ۚ وَمَا تُنفِقُوا۟ مِن شَىْءٍۢ فَإِنَّ ٱللَّهَ بِهِۦ عَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"[But as for you, O believers,] never shall you attain to true piety unless you spend on others out of what you cherish yourselves; and whatever you spend - verily, God has full knowledge thereof.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/385.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":68770,"position":1,"arabic":"لَن","translation":"কক্ষনো না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68771,"position":2,"arabic":"تَنَالُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা পাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68772,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْبِرَّ","translation":"কল্যাণ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68773,"position":4,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","translation":"যতক্ষণ না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68774,"position":5,"arabic":"تُنفِقُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা খরচ করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68775,"position":6,"arabic":"مِمَّا","translation":"তা থেকে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68776,"position":7,"arabic":"تُحِبُّونَ ۚ","translation":"তোমার ভালোবাস","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68778,"position":8,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং যা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68779,"position":9,"arabic":"تُنفِقُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা খরচ কর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68780,"position":10,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"(থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68781,"position":11,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","translation":"কোন কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68782,"position":12,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68783,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68784,"position":14,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"সে সম্পর্কে আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68785,"position":15,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"খুব অবগত","audioUrl":"wbw/003_092_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68786,"position":16,"arabic":"٩٢","translation":"(৯২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":93,"arabic":"۞ كُلُّ ٱلطَّعَامِ كَانَ حِلًّۭا لِّبَنِىٓ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ إِلَّا مَا حَرَّمَ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلُ عَلَىٰ نَفْسِهِۦ مِن قَبْلِ أَن تُنَزَّلَ ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةُ ۗ قُلْ فَأْتُوا۟ بِٱلتَّوْرَىٰةِ فَٱتْلُوهَآ إِن كُنتُمْ صَٰدِقِينَ","translation":"ALL FOOD was lawful unto the children of Israel, save what Israel had made unlawful unto itself [by its sinning] before the Torah was bestowed from on high. Say: \"Come forward, then, with the Torah and recite it, if what you say is true!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/386.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":69218,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ كُلُّ","translation":"সব","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69219,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلطَّعَامِ","translation":"খাদ্য","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69220,"position":3,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"ছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69221,"position":4,"arabic":"حِلًّۭا","translation":"হালাল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69222,"position":5,"arabic":"لِّبَنِىٓ","translation":"জন্য বনী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69223,"position":6,"arabic":"إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ","translation":"ইসরাঈলের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69224,"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69225,"position":8,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69226,"position":9,"arabic":"حَرَّمَ","translation":"হারাম করেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69227,"position":10,"arabic":"إِسْرَٰٓءِيلُ","translation":"ইসরাঈল (হযরত ইয়াকুব আঃ)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69228,"position":11,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69229,"position":12,"arabic":"نَفْسِهِۦ","translation":"তার নিজের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69230,"position":13,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"(থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69231,"position":14,"arabic":"قَبْلِ","translation":"পূর্বে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69232,"position":15,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"(যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69233,"position":16,"arabic":"تُنَزَّلَ","translation":"নাযিল হওয়ার","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69234,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةُ ۗ","translation":"তাওরাত","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69236,"position":18,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"তুমি বল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69237,"position":19,"arabic":"فَأْتُوا۟","translation":"''তবে তোমরা আন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69238,"position":20,"arabic":"بِٱلتَّوْرَىٰةِ","translation":"তাওরাত","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69239,"position":21,"arabic":"فَٱتْلُوهَآ","translation":"তোমরা অতঃপর পাঠ কর তা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69240,"position":22,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69241,"position":23,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা হও","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69242,"position":24,"arabic":"صَـٰدِقِينَ","translation":"সত্যবাদী''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_093_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69243,"position":25,"arabic":"٩٣","translation":"(৯৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":94,"arabic":"فَمَنِ ٱفْتَرَىٰ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ ٱلْكَذِبَ مِنۢ بَعْدِ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلظَّٰلِمُونَ","translation":"And all who henceforth invent lies about God - it is they, they who are evildoers!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/387.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":69636,"position":1,"arabic":"فَمَنِ","translation":"যে অতঃপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69637,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱفْتَرَىٰ","translation":"আরোপ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69638,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69639,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69640,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْكَذِبَ","translation":"মিথ্যা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69641,"position":6,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"(থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69642,"position":7,"arabic":"بَعْدِ","translation":"পরেও","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69643,"position":8,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69644,"position":9,"arabic":"فَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","translation":"ফলে ঐ সব লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69645,"position":10,"arabic":"هُمُ","translation":"তারাই","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69646,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمُونَ","translation":"জালিম","audioUrl":"wbw/003_094_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69647,"position":12,"arabic":"٩٤","translation":"(৯৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":95,"arabic":"قُلْ صَدَقَ ٱللَّهُ ۗ فَٱتَّبِعُوا۟ مِلَّةَ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ حَنِيفًۭا وَمَا كَانَ مِنَ ٱلْمُشْرِكِينَ","translation":"Say: \"God has spoken the truth: follow, then, the creed of Abraham, who turned away from all that is false, and was not of those who ascribe divinity to aught beside God.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/388.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":69903,"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"তুমি বল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69904,"position":2,"arabic":"صَدَقَ","translation":"সত্য বলেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69905,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۗ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69907,"position":4,"arabic":"فَٱتَّبِعُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা অতঃপর অনুসরণ কর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69908,"position":5,"arabic":"مِلَّةَ","translation":"পন্থা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69909,"position":6,"arabic":"إِبْرَٰهِيمَ","translation":"ইব্রাহীমের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69910,"position":7,"arabic":"حَنِيفًۭا","translation":"একমুখী হয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69911,"position":8,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69912,"position":9,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"সে ছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69913,"position":10,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69914,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْمُشْرِكِينَ","translation":"মুশরিকদের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_095_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69915,"position":12,"arabic":"٩٥","translation":"(৯৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":96,"arabic":"إِنَّ أَوَّلَ بَيْتٍۢ وُضِعَ لِلنَّاسِ لَلَّذِى بِبَكَّةَ مُبَارَكًۭا وَهُدًۭى لِّلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translation":"Behold, the first Temple ever set up for mankind was indeed the one at Bakkah: rich in blessing, and a [source of] guidance unto all the worlds,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/389.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":70189,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70190,"position":2,"arabic":"أَوَّلَ","translation":"প্রথম","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70191,"position":3,"arabic":"بَيْتٍۢ","translation":"ঘর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70192,"position":4,"arabic":"وُضِعَ","translation":"তৈরি করা হয়েছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70193,"position":5,"arabic":"لِلنَّاسِ","translation":"লোকদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70194,"position":6,"arabic":"لَلَّذِى","translation":"যা অবশ্যই","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70195,"position":7,"arabic":"بِبَكَّةَ","translation":"মক্কায় (অবস্থিত)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70196,"position":8,"arabic":"مُبَارَكًۭا","translation":"বরকতময়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70197,"position":9,"arabic":"وَهُدًۭى","translation":"ও হিদায়াতের (কেন্দ্র)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70198,"position":10,"arabic":"لِّلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","translation":"বিশ্ববাসীদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/003_096_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70199,"position":11,"arabic":"٩٦","translation":"(৯৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":97,"arabic":"فِيهِ ءَايَٰتٌۢ بَيِّنَٰتٌۭ مَّقَامُ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ ۖ وَمَن دَخَلَهُۥ كَانَ ءَامِنًۭا ۗ وَلِلَّهِ عَلَى ٱلنَّاسِ حِجُّ ٱلْبَيْتِ مَنِ ٱسْتَطَاعَ إِلَيْهِ سَبِيلًۭا ۚ وَمَن كَفَرَ فَإِنَّ ٱللَّهَ غَنِىٌّ عَنِ ٱلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translation":"full of clear messages. [It is] the place whereon Abraham once stood; and whoever enters it finds inner peace. Hence, pilgrimage unto the Temple is a duty owed to God by all people who are able to undertake it. And as for those who deny the truth - verily, God does not stand in need of anything in all the worlds.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/390.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":70524,"position":1,"arabic":"فِيهِ","translation":"তার মধ্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70525,"position":2,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتٌۢ","translation":"নিদর্শনাবলী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70526,"position":3,"arabic":"بَيِّنَـٰتٌۭ","translation":"সুস্পষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70527,"position":4,"arabic":"مَّقَامُ","translation":"মাকামে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70528,"position":5,"arabic":"إِبْرَٰهِيمَ ۖ","translation":"ইব্রাহীম","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70530,"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"এবং যে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70531,"position":7,"arabic":"دَخَلَهُۥ","translation":"তাতে প্রবেশ করল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70532,"position":8,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"সে হল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70533,"position":9,"arabic":"ءَامِنًۭا ۗ","translation":"নিরাপদ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70535,"position":10,"arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহরই জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70536,"position":11,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70537,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسِ","translation":"লোকদের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70538,"position":13,"arabic":"حِجُّ","translation":"হজ্জ করা (ফরজ)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_097_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70539,